  dialogueLines:
  - 'Good morrow! '
  - 'Oh my brother sent you? '
  - 'You''re looking for the key to the back gate? '
  - 'Yeah I know where it is. '
  - 'It''s at the old man''s house right down this path. '
  - 'But I think the gate to get to it was locked by some magic spell when the Mother
    disappeared. '
  - 'I think the alchemist will have some information on how to unlock it.  '
  - Their shop is right next to the butcher's shop on the main way.
